    "Whiskers are chosen to show the 1.5 of the interquartile range.",
    "Up-triangles denote the minima and downtriangles denote the maxima.",
    "b Podium plots for visualizing the performance correspondence of 60 external validation tasks.",
    "Upper part: each colored dot denotes the median DSC achieved with the respective method on one task.",
    "Dots corresponding to identical tasks are connected by a line."
